&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is a Consultant post based in Cwm Taf Morgannwg University Health Board for Rehabilitation Services and you will be joining Colleagues in a very dynamic and forward looking Directorate, with supportive colleagues and a culture where development and progression is embedded. The Postholder will be managerially responsible to Dr Kishore Kale, Clinical Director. The Postholder will be required to liaise with Clinicians as and when necessary. Further the Postholder will be expected work at other UHB Sites and elsewhere in the Community including Patients homes from time to time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Kishore Kale&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clinical Director/Consultant Psychiatrist&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Mental Health unit&lt;/p&gt;
